# APIs

## GET /value/search

Search for a value



### Parameters

| Name | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| value | string | False | Search for a value in field *value* |


### Responses

#### 200


OK




#### 250


Nothing found




#### 251


Invalid search
